{"tid":790452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[新聞嚟架?] 酒樓變擂台 禿頭阿伯激戰兩阿姐","createTime":"2018-08-23T04:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T04:51:13.000Z","uid":44562,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0ec045125bfa57db030b9ad4c3bee060eae4f297","tid":790452,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T04:17:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180823/58596157\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180823%2F58596157&d=h7c0o%2BmwdMUlfomTdpq4wTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=73e7b854\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180823%2F58596157&h=d628c78e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180823/58596157</a><br />\n<br />\n事發時係7點43分左右，阿姐同位光頭阿伯講到好勞氣，仲手指指，而嗰位光頭阿伯應該係一個人黎，同一位阿姐搭枱坐，嘈嘈吓，光頭阿伯首先發爛拎起茶杯掟向阿姐，阿姐亦不甘示弱，快手咁拎起另一個杯，將茶潑向對方，拿，大戰正式開始！<br />\n<br />\n附近茶客爭相走避，就咁你掟我，我掟你，光頭阿伯最終竟然擸起茶壺向阿姐個頭扑埋去，一時間，茶壺變咗武器，喺場內亂飛，呢個時候，一位黃衣熱心阿叔行埋去從後抱住光頭阿叔，酒樓一位「架兩」阿姐亦加入勸交，光頭阿叔一度想擸櫈掟人，好彩熱心男拉住咋，而阿姐就乘機走人，但「架兩」阿姐講講吓竟然激動起上黎，加入戰團，仲起腳踢光頭阿叔！媽啊！好亂啊！<br />\n<br />\n畀兩個女人打，光頭阿叔激到爆炸，喺地下拎起茶壺繼續發動攻勢，狠狠哋兜頭扑落「架兩」阿姐，之後就氣沖沖咁行埋一邊，大戰結束，一班茶客睇到呆晒，真係嚇都嚇飽！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啲記者寫開咩小說架 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75e5651223e9915e05ee4a444a8d46d5af66b671","tid":790452,"uid":14065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T04:18:12.000Z","msg":"外賣仔嬌喘一聲"},{"pid":"c72b81852b290c76693dd1924879e2919090a302","tid":790452,"uid":34685,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T04:23:43.000Z","msg":"擂台上鬼影重重"},{"pid":"5405bae1a16af04afd65a1d22dc4fc951292f78d","tid":790452,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T04:28:11.000Z","msg":"阿姐不慌不忙渾圓成盾，使出乾坤大挪移<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5befa9b9f4be254baa2a8bd552dbe261e94dd1dc","tid":790452,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75e5651223e9915e05ee4a444a8d46d5af66b671","tid":790452,"uid":14065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T04:18:12.000Z","msg":"外賣仔嬌喘一聲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T04:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae60d9ec0f79d87616ed1e0350c5d9e6a59767e8","tid":790452,"uid":44562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5befa9b9f4be254baa2a8bd552dbe261e94dd1dc","tid":790452,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75e5651223e9915e05ee4a444a8d46d5af66b671","tid":790452,"uid":14065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T04:18:12.000Z","msg":"外賣仔嬌喘一聲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T04:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T04:36:04.000Z","msg":"唔是大師兄咩 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf136419ce93c18c8cb62bb3a9f01fdae801f88","tid":790452,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae60d9ec0f79d87616ed1e0350c5d9e6a59767e8","tid":790452,"uid":44562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5befa9b9f4be254baa2a8bd552dbe261e94dd1dc","tid":790452,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75e5651223e9915e05ee4a444a8d46d5af66b671","tid":790452,"uid":14065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T04:18:12.000Z","msg":"外賣仔嬌喘一聲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T04:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T04:36:04.000Z","msg":"唔是大師兄咩 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T04:37:51.000Z","msg":"外賣仔嬌喘一聲倒在外賣仔的懷裡"},{"pid":"a273e6e3f3d4782b03bb3b200eb90e2d5550c238","tid":790452,